songs.title: 1987 Vette
songs.lyrics:
[Intro]
Lemme show you what this shit can do
Where my motherfuckin' car keys?
Okay, let's go

[Verse 1]
Eighty-seven vette, through the city I'm mashin' (Yeah)
It ain't for sale, baby, man, this shit is a classic
This a million-dollar meetin' (Yeah), but I'm keepin' it casual
Baby, anything is possible and I'm the example (Oh yeah)
Bounced out the valet (Valet) lookin' all suave (Suave)
I was playin' Sade (Sade), cute lil' shawty (Ayy)
I was in the A with it, just a couple days with it (Shit)
Bust a couple plays with it, bucket like A's Boogie
Had to learn the hard way (Yeah), but I'm still thankful, though (Yeah)
I don't need a gun on me, respected everywhere I go (Ayy)
I don't need a nigga ho, I got too many of those
I'm on the San Mateo bridge, we just left Hayward, though (I'm on my way)
Baby lookin' like a snack, I'ma need a piece of that (Piece of that)
Lemme know your off days and baby, I can handle that
I been on my fuckin' grind, they tryna knock me off of that
No jewelry on (Yeah) but, baby, this my own fitted cap
What's happenin'?

[Chorus]
Baby, why you playin' with me? (Playin' with me)
You ain't goin' home tonight, love, you stayin' with me
For real, what's happenin'?
You been lookin' all night, you low-key, just how I like it
Quit playin', what's happenin'?
What's happenin'? (What's happenin'?)
What's happenin'? Damn (What's happenin'?)
I see you lookin', baby, so what's happenin'?
(What's happenin'?) Ay, ay, ay, what's happenin'?
Yeah, what's happenin'?
Off top (What's happenin'?)

[Verse 2]
Beatin' up the blade, all stock on the pavement (Uh)
Trip down south got the bitch eatin' Cajun
Thirty-six milli Rolex goin' apeshit (For real)
I'm feelin' like Pac around when Brenda had the baby (Ayy)
I used to drive that all-gray 0-2 Mercedes
My radio was trippin', but them hoes still paid me
Mackin' all sudden in this Cartier bracelet
Hit a nigga line one time, you been playin'

[Chorus]
What's happenin'? (What's happenin'?)
What's happenin'? (What's happenin'?)
Damn, what's happenin'?
I see you lookin', baby, so what's happenin'?
(What's happenin'?) Ay, ay, ay, what's happenin'?
Yeah, what's happenin'?
Off top (What's happenin'?)
Baby, why you playin' with me? (Playin' with me)
You ain't goin' home tonight, love, you stayin' with me
For real, what's happenin'?
You been lookin' all night, you low-key, just how I like it
Quit playin', what's happenin'?
What's happenin'? (What's happenin'?)
What's happenin'? Damn (What's happenin'?)
I see you lookin', baby, so what's happenin'?
(What's happenin'?) Ay, ay, ay, what's happenin'?
Yeah, what's happenin'?
Off top (What's happenin'?)
